48402520: Please complete the following fields to become a signatory for an RSO, CalGreeks student organization, or ASUC/GA Unit. Read the instructions below carefully!
There are up to eight fields for you to input the organization names and IDs of which you intend to be a Signatory. The first two fields are required, you may leave the other fields blank once completing your organization's information. You will get a warning message from the course that some of the fields are blank, but you can ignore and hit SUBMIT. If you're a signatory for more than 8 organizations, please email OASIS at studentorgadvising@berkeley.edu to discuss accommodating additional organizations. Remember to press submit at the end of this quiz.
If you encounter issues, please fill out the Signatory Issues Form and our team will investigate and reach out to you within 3 business days.

48402519: For RSOs  Cal Greeks:
In order to complete this next section, you will need your organization's complete name as it appears in CalLink and your organization ID number. Below is OASIS's list of organizations and their corresponding Callink Org ID numbers. Please find your org(s) name and ID number by scrolling or searching this list. You may also find the link to this list here.

ASUC/GA Units ONLY:
ASUC/GA Unit names do NOT appear in the list below. Please refer to your Callink page, and copy the name of your office/program/commission as it appears there. ASUC/GA Units will input a "0" for Org ID.
